posting_body: ['1215 Laguna at Eddy', 'Call Jeff at', 'show contact info', 'to set up a showing.', 'OPN SAT 10-11', 'Great corner studio with brand new kitchen $2300', 'Spacious East facing apartment ...$2250..  for a apartment available at the end of August.', 'Marina style corner building .....', 'All just remodeled ...... very nice!!!!', 'Huge studio with walk-in closet', 'Sunny with Sun and light from the East, South and West depending on the apartment', 'Large eat in kitchen w/ gas stove and NEW refrigerator', 'Elevator and Laundry', 'Walking distance to Japantown, The Fillmore, Civic Center and Hayes Valley great  shops etc. including:  Matcha” - the terrific soft serve ice cream shop in the Japantown mall.', ' The grocery store there is consistently rated one of the best in the city.', ' Not to mention outstanding Ramen and Sushi options.', 'Public transportation outside the front door.....', '31 bus goes down to the financial district to south of market and goes the other way to USF and the beach .....it crosses all the major bus lines in the city', 'Easy street parking.', 'Several square blocks of parks across the street w/ tennis courts, ball fields, basketball courts etc.', 'TEXT David at', 'show contact info', 'for a video', 'Sorry, NO PETS and No Smoking']
